Ing '''''Minecraft''''' metung yang pyalung a [[open world|sandbox]] [[indie]]ng minunang lelangan ning programmer a Swedish a i [[Markus Persson|Markus "Notch" Persson]], at kaybat inalkus na ampong linimbag ning [[Mojang]]. Mipalwal ya para king malda para king [[Personal computer|PC]] anyang Mayo 17, 2009, antimong bersyong [[Video game development#Alpha|alpha]] at, kaybat da reng ditak-ditak a pamagbayu, milimbag ya antimong ganap a bersyong ganap pamagpalwal (''full release version'') anyang Noviembre 18, 2011. Pabulan bayu ita, mipalwal ya ing metung a bersyon para king [[Android (operating system)|Android]] anyang Octubre 7, at mipalwal ya ing metung a bersyong para king [[iOS]] anyang Noviembre 17, 2011. Kanitang Mayo 9, 2012, pepalwal de ing pyalung para king [[Xbox 360]] antimong pyalung a [[Xbox Live Arcade]], a miyalkus kayabe ya ing [[4J Studios]]. Atin lang pamagbayu andat kayi deng anggang bersyon ning ''Minecraft''. 

Kapamilatan da reng aspetu nang makudta ampong pang-pamanikdo (''creative and building aspects'') ning ''Minecraft'', makapanikdo la reng mamyalung a manikdo manibat kareng medukit a kubo (''textured cubes'') king yatung [[3D computer graphics|3D]] ampong [[procedural generation|procedurally generated]]. Kayabe kareng aliwang malyaring gawan king pyalung ing pamaglakbe, pamanipun bandi (''gathering resources''), pamaglalang ampong pamakilaban. Ketang pangapalwal o ''release'' nang komersyal, adwa la reng kaparalanan o ''modes'': [[survival mode|survival]], nung nu la mangaylangang manipun bandi deng mamyalung at magmantini king karelang kabulasan (''[[health (gaming)|health]]'') ampong [[danup]]; ampong makudta o ''[[#Creative mode|creative]]'', nung nu alang angga ing mibibye kareng mamyalung a bandi, atin lang kagiwan a sulagpo, at ala lang prublema king kabulasan o danup. Ating katlung kaparalanan o ''mode'' a pareu king ''survival'', at aliwa mu kaniti king sákit; makakana ya king pekamasákit a ''setting'' o pangabili at e malyari ing pamanganak o  it is set to hardest setting and ''respawning'', anya mapipilitan la reng mamyalung a ilako la reng karelang yatu o ''world'' kamate da. 

Mirinan yang limang galal ing ''Minecraft'' anyang 2011 [[Game Developers Conference]]: mika galal yang Innovation Award, Best Downloadable Game Award, ampong Best Debut Game Award ibat king [[Game Developers Choice Awards]]; ampo ing Audience Award, pati na ing Seumas McNally Grand Prize, ibat king [[Independent Games Festival]] anyang 2011. Kanitang 2012, mika galal yang [[Golden Joystick Award]] ing ''Minecraft'' king kategoryang Best Downloadable Game.<ref name="CVG Golden Joystick"/> Anyang Enero 22, 2013, maygit nong syam a milyung kopya ning pyalung ing misali kng PC ampong maygit 20 (adwang pulung) milyun kareng aliwang plataporma.<ref name="Minecraft Sales hit 20 Million">{{cite web | url=http://www.vg247.com/2013/01/22/minecraft-sales-hit-20-million-mark-for-all-platforms/ | title=Minecraft sales hit 20 million mark for all platforms | date=January 22, 2013 | work = [[VG247]] | accessdate=January 30, 2013 | author=Nunneley, Stephany}}</ref>

